DEPLOY BACKEND (Render + GitHub Actions)
=======================================

Mục tiêu
- Tự động deploy backend từ GitHub lên Render mỗi khi push lên branch main.

Yeu cau
1) Tai khoan Render
2) Du an da push len GitHub (branch main)
3) Backend nam trong thu muc: backend/
4) Repo da co file: .github/workflows/backend-deploy.yml

Buoc 1: Tao Web Service tren Render
1. Dang nhap Render Dashboard.
2. New -> Web Service.
3. Chon repo GitHub cua ban.
4. Root Directory: backend
5. Build Command: npm install
6. Start Command: npm start
7. Plan: Free
8. Create Web Service.

Buoc 2: Lay Deploy Hook URL
1. Vao Render -> Web Service -> Settings.
2. Tim muc "Deploy Hook".
3. Create Deploy Hook va copy URL.

Buoc 3: Tao GitHub Secret
1. Vao repo GitHub -> Settings -> Secrets and variables -> Actions.
2. New repository secret:
   - RENDER_DEPLOY_HOOK_URL : URL deploy hook o buoc 2

Buoc 4: Kiem tra workflow
File: .github/workflows/backend-deploy.yml
Noi dung can co (tom tat):
- Goi curl POST toi RENDER_DEPLOY_HOOK_URL

Neu da giong, bo qua buoc nay.

Buoc 5: Push len GitHub
1. Commit code moi nhat.
2. Push len branch main.

Buoc 6: Kiem tra Actions
1. Vao tab Actions trong repo.
2. Chon workflow "Deploy Backend to Heroku".
3. Doi job chay xong (green).

Buoc 7: Kiem tra app
1. Vao Render -> Web Service -> Open.
2. Duong dan mac dinh: https://<TEN_SERVICE>.onrender.com

Test nhanh
- Mo trang tao link: https://<TEN_SERVICE>.onrender.com/
- Tao link, truy cap: https://<TEN_SERVICE>.onrender.com/c/<id>

Luu y
- Render free co the sleep, lan dau mo se cham.
- Neu loi, xem log:
  Render Dashboard -> Logs
